RT by @ZhouFengSuo: Hearing Notice | On Thursday, @ChinaSelect will have a hearing entitled, "China's Campaign to Steal America's AI Edge." 

The discussion will focus on what China can buy vs. what China attempts to steal when legal acquisition falls short. Topics will include SME and AI chips, foundry evasion, chip smuggling, adversarial distillation of frontier U.S. models, and more.

